      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for libvirt fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2024-2494: Fixed negative g_new0 length can lead to unbounded memory allocation (bsc#1221815).\n",
